<br />\n反而而家做野講野都要諗過度過先 仲要唔好比位人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387dcf157c97458ca4f458bcc50e46cac8374bac","tid":331682,"uid":22425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"果時成日想快d大個出黎返工搵錢 想買乜就買乜 又唔駛再溫書考試做功課<br />\n<br />\n到宜家出黎做野 日日做重複既工作 朋友都少見左<br />\n又會懷念以前 果種無憂無慮 每日都見到自己既朋友 hehe哈哈既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前係心靈上快樂 冇物質 宜家係有物質 但就失去心靈上既快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8361c4c43dda90bc81574b083830694a3c5c9e","tid":331682,"uid":114124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"有 <br />\n咁岩頭先睇返舊電話入面嘅中學相<br />\n再同啲fd講返起以前啲好笑野<br />\n就覺得時間真係過得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99afc1c895f04385a3f2538053cba3858b0f6e79","tid":331682,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n以前落堂仲要做功課溫書<br />\n依家收工就睇戲食飯打機<br />\n起碼叫有屬於自己的時間<br />\n覺得返工好過讀書又有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你翻工唔攰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1, 返工真係正過返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀書時chur大個搵到hea工<br />\n讀書hea大個做chur工<br />\n一般黎睇</blockquote><br />\n好純情既諗法</blockquote><br />\n一般=/=all</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成績同工作能力冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nkong u first hon另計</blockquote><br />\nHku 1st hon就唔使chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57ee89c