63","tid":331682,"uid":90207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T22:02:10.000Z","msg":"整個求學時期嚟睇，我自己覺得asso生活最開心<br />\n我讀冷門科，個班嘅規模超細，嚟嚟去去都係嗰廿幾個同學<br />\n但係大家都真心對嗰科有興趣，又各自有擅長嘅興趣、專長<br />\n除咗一兩個特別仆街之外，可以話成班同聲同氣<br />\n上堂嗰時就大家一齊學學術嘢，閒時就大家各流吓自己擅長嘅嘢，或者一齊食吓飯咁<br />\n原本就熟嘅當然會彼此close啲，但絕對無排外同喺人哋背後講人壞話嘅小圈子<br />\n反而一齊俾班商科撚喺背後話阻住地球轉就試過<br />\n最後我就上咗ugc degree，同學就走晒<br />\n上堂人來人往，其他人唔會主動同你講嘢<br />\n嗰時係完全唔識人咁滯<br />\n讀咗兩年degree就嚟grad先識到三四個講到吓嘢嘅同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a7d81adfcef6e1e5bbb8f29cda569a2dfdaf4c","tid":331682,"uid":93588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T22:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee818b733f1481e84d81781aa070e7fa078280a1","tid":331682,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"係人都唔想返工架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1daf86cb3c969022529a6d06c78f27d9e7b14a1d","tid":331682,"uid":33631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T01:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係人都唔想返工架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c217d462f8005e49746057a5e2268a283606dd","tid":331682,"uid":111019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今年廿幾歲<br />\n大學都離開左幾年<br />\n每日都營營役役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一邊搵錢生活 <br />\n一邊比社會欺壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望番轉頭<br />\n中學時期既回憶有笑有淚 <br />\n有毒撚追女仔 得閒又整蠱下老師同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" c